reviewText: I loved this 25 minute movie since I first started watching Garfield A+
The "video" arrived on time and in great condition. We had a movie night with our kids and grandkids. This was a favorite episode when our kids were growing up.

Garfield takes to the streets in this Emmy award-winning special.  Out on the town, the famous feline encounters long-lost relatives and some really "bad" cats.  Garfield go home!
Great movie! A+!
